  "description": "Pi constant at depth 5 — deep into the irrational. Partials spread very flat (all near 0.2) so no single partial dominates — the result is a diffuse spectral mist. Long attack dissolves the note into air. Very high resonator mix creates an atmospheric chamber that outlives the note. The mathematics of Pi made fog.",
